The,Metrc,Marijuana,Enforcement,Tracking,Reporting,Compliance,Web,API,allows,developers,to,interact,with,the,Metrc,regulatory,compliance,system,The,API,can,pull,information,from,Metrc,into,a,point,of,sale,system,The,API,supports,the,pulling,of,the,following,information,Facilities,Harvests,Items,Packages,Patients,Plant,Groups,Plants,Rooms,Sales,Transactions,Strains,and,Units,of,Measure,UoM,It,uses,a,RESTful,architecture,with,requests,and,responses,formatted,in,JSON